{% extends 'layout.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}
    Web development and design
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

<div role="main" class="main">
    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <ul class="breadcrumb">
                        <li><a href='{{ path('_home') }}'>Home</a></li>
                        <li class="active">Portfolio</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="owl-carousel owl-theme" data-plugin-options='{"items": 1, "margin": 10, "autoplay": "true"}'>
                    <div>
                        <span class="img-thumbnail">
                            <img alt="html-css-js" height="300" class="img-responsive" src="{{ asset('img/skills/html-css-js.jpg') }}">
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="img-thumbnail">
                            <img alt="php-mysql" height="300" class="img-responsive" src="{{ asset('img/skills/php-mysql.jpg') }}">
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="img-thumbnail">
                            <img alt="symfony" height="300" class="img-responsive" src="{{ asset('img/skills/symfony.jpg') }}">
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="img-thumbnail">
                            <img alt="adobe" height="300" class="img-responsive" src="{{ asset('img/skills/adobe.jpg') }}">
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">


                <p>
                    I learned web development at the very prestigious <a href="https://3wa.fr/" target="_blank">3W Academy</a>
                    in Paris. Their pedagogical approach is very interesting, as I was first taught the basis of HTML and CSS and later on,
                    I was introduced to the wonders of javascript, Php and Mysql. The 3W Academy, had a particular focus on object
                    oriented programming and teaching the
                    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Model%E2%80%93view%E2%80%93controller" target="_blank"> MVC architecture</a>, which is a very
                    clean and smart way of developing websites. Over time I started learning and using some interesting tools like
                    <a href="https://symfony.com/" target="_blank" >symfony</a> (a Frenchie Php framework),
                    <a href="http://gulpjs.com/" target="_blank" >Gulp</a> (an incredible tool to minimize JS and CSS http requests) and
                    <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/" target="_blank" >Bootstrap</a> (the fastest way to have a nice front end).
                    I have also played and written a few scripts for my sites in <a href="https://www.python.org/" target="_blank">Python</a>
                    and <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank">NodeJs</a>, just for the fun of it !
                    </br>
                    I am a self learner and some of the technical challenges, I've needed to solve on my own while working on my websites, include:
                </p>
                <ul class="list list-icons">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Defining a smart architecture for multilingual websites</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Displaying GeoJson data in Google maps</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Web Scrapping</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Using external apis (such as twilio, twitter, google, etc)</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <hr>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-xlg">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="circular-bar">
                    <div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="90" data-plugin-options='{"barColor": "#E36159"}'>
                        <strong>Php/MySql</strong>
                        <label><span class="percent">90</span>%</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="circular-bar">
                    <div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="70" data-plugin-options='{"barColor": "#0088CC", "delay": 300}'>
                        <strong>Symfony</strong>
                        <label><span class="percent">70</span>%</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="circular-bar">
                    <div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="75" data-plugin-options='{"barColor": "#2BAAB1", "delay": 600}'>
                        <strong>Javascript</strong>
                        <label><span class="percent">75</span>%</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="circular-bar">
                    <div class="circular-bar-chart" data-percent="95" data-plugin-options='{"barColor": "#353535", "delay": 900}'>
                        <strong>Graphic design</strong>
                        <label><span class="percent">95</span>%</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <h2>Portfolio</h2>
        <p>Besides from being a web developer, I am also a graphic designer and I've worked on the branding and image of different companies and projects</p>

        <ul class="nav nav-pills sort-source" data-sort-id="portfolio" data-option-key="filter">
            <li data-option-value="*" class="active"><a href="#">Show All</a></li>
            <li data-option-value=".websites"><a href="#">Websites</a></li>
            <li data-option-value=".design"><a href="#">Design</a></li>
            <li data-option-value=".other"><a href="#">Other</a></li>
        </ul>

        <hr>

        <div class="row">

            <ul class="portfolio-list sort-destination" data-sort-id="portfolio">

                {% for projectName, project in portfolio %}


                    <li class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 isotope-item {{ project.category }}">
                        <div class="portfolio-item">
                            <a href="{{ ['portfolio/',project.name]|join }}">
                            <span class="thumb-info">
                                <span class="thumb-info-wrapper">
                                    <img src="{{ asset(['img/portfolio/',project.name,'-preview.jpg']|join) }}" class="img-responsive" alt="{{ [projectName, '_preview']|join }}">
                                    <span class="thumb-info-title">
                                        <span class="thumb-info-inner">{{ project.title }}</span>
                                        <span class="thumb-info-type">{{ project.type }}</span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span class="thumb-info-action">
                                        <span class="thumb-info-action-icon"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                {% endfor %}


            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}